title: Watch Fiona Apple Sing Frankie Valli & Stevie Wonder For Valentine’s Day
text: Last week, director Kevin Hayes shared a video of Fiona Apple singing an a cappella rendition of SWV's 1992 single "Weak." And now, to celebrate Valentine's Day, he's filmed two goofy videos of singing Frankie Valli's "Can't Take My Eyes Off You" and Stevie Wonder's "I Just Called To Say I Love You" karaoke-style … More »
